      "iconName": "Nether_Touch",
      "tips": "This passive is very useful when clearing out minion wave as well as harrassing an enemy in lane. This passive will be used effectively when you use \"Nether Snare\" in the middle of the minion wave. This will apply the passive on each minion and will eventually explode when the minion dies. The explosion covers a certain area that can damage the enemy health bar.",
