      "description": "Vexana summons an Eternal Guard at the target location, dealing 480 (+60% Total Magic Power) Magic Damage to enemies hit and knocking them airborne for 0.8s. The Eternal Guard then joins Vexana in battle for 15s. Each of the Eternal Guard's attacks deals 200 (+40% Total Magic Power) plus 5% of the target's Max HP as Magic Damage to enemies in a large area.",
